{"tid":1331480,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚食咗件大波粉嫩黑驚人妻","createTime":"2019-07-19T03:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T09:40:35.000Z","uid":14090,"like":49,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6b5fa77594cd3dbf5c3f7b4b022d50a10e47b0a2","tid":1331480,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:04:43.000Z","msg":"好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n估唔到條人妻話呢排佢老公太大壓力 所以硬唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要話我硬過警棍 屌 聽到呢到嬲嬲地咪用私家警棍扑落佢到囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你老婆又幾濕 搞到成張床都濕哂 希望你唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思囉pc仔 你老婆係幾好砌 唔知係咪餓咗好耐 又淫又多水 仲要中出咗幾鑊 十個月後生咗件唔好多謝我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提 去狗屋附近開下we7 扮下住家男 大把人妻想含<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fedc2c202e7481c4c014d65ccac89ad8012f958","tid":1331480,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:12:33.000Z","msg":"睇實啲你老婆啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374968d1655a06811a89bccae89cc3301305e0f5","tid":1331480,"uid":57797,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:18:15.000Z","msg":"作家呀作家，幻想完未呀？ 作文都作好d 丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96bfda8983b6678a1d55909856fdfd16c0a929c","tid":1331480,"uid":42487,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:19:58.000Z","msg":"俾D誠意<br />\n是但偷張圖都要掛..."},{"pid":"5a8aceefd442a5011d5c8279671fc61be322ded8","tid":1331480,"uid":14090,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a96bfda8983b6678a1d55909856fdfd16c0a929c","tid":1331480,"uid":42487,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:19:58.000Z","msg":"俾D誠意<br />\n是但偷張圖都要掛..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:24:37.000Z",